description:
Linus Torvalds announced the general availability of the first Release Candidate version of the upcoming Linux 6.10 kernel series for public testing.

The post Linus Torvalds Announces First Linux Kernel 6.10 Release Candidate appeared first on 9to5Linux - do not reproduce this article without permission. This RSS feed is intended for readers, not scrapers.
title: Linus Torvalds Announces First Linux Kernel 6.10 Release Candidate
